{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"So, I was in the hospital for a long time."},{"time":4000,"text":"And a few years after I left, I went back,"},{"time":7000,"text":"and the chairman of the burn department was very excited to see me --"},{"time":10000,"text":"said, \"Dan, I have a fantastic new treatment for you.\""},{"time":13000,"text":"I was very excited. I walked with him to his office."},{"time":15000,"text":"And he explained to me that, when I shave,"},{"time":18000,"text":"I have little black dots on the left side of my face where the hair is,"},{"time":21000,"text":"but on the right side of my face"},{"time":23000,"text":"I was badly burned so I have no hair,"},{"time":25000,"text":"and this creates lack of symmetry."},{"time":27000,"text":"And what's the brilliant idea he had?"},{"time":29000,"text":"He was going to tattoo little black dots"},{"time":31000,"text":"on the right side of my face"},{"time":34000,"text":"and make me look very symmetric."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36000,"text":"It sounded interesting. He asked me to go and shave."},{"time":39000,"text":"Let me tell you, this was a strange way to shave,"},{"time":41000,"text":"because I thought about it"},{"time":43000,"text":"and I realized that the way I was shaving then"},{"time":45000,"text":"would be the way I would shave for the rest of my life --"},{"time":47000,"text":"because I had to keep the width the same."},{"time":49000,"text":"When I got back to his office,"},{"time":51000,"text":"I wasn't really sure."},{"time":53000,"text":"I said, \"Can I see some evidence for this?\""},{"time":55000,"text":"So he showed me some pictures"},{"time":57000,"text":"of little cheeks with little black dots --"},{"time":59000,"text":"not very informative."},{"time":61000,"text":"I said, \"What happens when I grow older and my hair becomes white?"},{"time":63000,"text":"What would happen then?\""},{"time":65000,"text":"\"Oh, don't worry about it,\" he said."},{"time":67000,"text":"\"We have lasers; we can whiten it out.\""},{"time":70000,"text":"But I was still concerned,"},{"time":72000,"text":"so I said, \"You know what, I'm not going to do it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":75000,"text":"And then came one of the biggest guilt trips of my life."},{"time":79000,"text":"This is coming from a Jewish guy, all right, so that means a lot."},{"time":82000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":84000,"text":"And he said, \"Dan, what's wrong with you?"},{"time":87000,"text":"Do you enjoy looking non-symmetric?"},{"time":89000,"text":"Do you have some kind of perverted pleasure from this?"},{"time":94000,"text":"Do women feel pity for you"},{"time":96000,"text":"and have sex with you more frequently?\""},{"time":99000,"text":"None of those happened."},{"time":103000,"text":"And this was very surprising to me,"},{"time":105000,"text":"because I've gone through many treatments --"},{"time":107000,"text":"there were many treatments I decided not to do --"},{"time":109000,"text":"and I never got this guilt trip to this extent."},{"time":111000,"text":"But I decided not to have this treatment."},{"time":113000,"text":"And I went to his deputy and asked him, \"What was going on?"},{"time":115000,"text":"Where was this guilt trip coming from?\""},{"time":117000,"text":"And he explained that they have done this procedure on two patients already,"},{"time":121000,"text":"and they need the third patient for a paper they were writing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"Now you probably think that this guy's a schmuck."},{"time":128000,"text":"Right, that's what he seems like."},{"time":130000,"text":"But let me give you a different perspective on the same story."},{"time":133000,"text":"A few years ago, I was running some of my own experiments in the lab."},{"time":136000,"text":"And when we run experiments,"},{"time":138000,"text":"we usually hope that one group will behave differently than another."},{"time":141000,"text":"So we had one group that I hoped their performance would be very high,"},{"time":144000,"text":"another group that I thought their performance would be very low,"},{"time":147000,"text":"and when I got the results, that's what we got --"},{"time":149000,"text":"I was very happy -- aside from one person."},{"time":152000,"text":"There was one person in the group"},{"time":154000,"text":"that was supposed to have very high performance"},{"time":156000,"text":"that was actually performing terribly."},{"time":158000,"text":"And he pulled the whole mean down,"},{"time":160000,"text":"destroying my statistical significance of the test."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"So I looked carefully at this guy."},{"time":166000,"text":"He was 20-some years older than anybody else in the sample."},{"time":169000,"text":"And I remembered that the old and drunken guy"},{"time":171000,"text":"came one day to the lab"},{"time":173000,"text":"wanting to make some easy cash"},{"time":175000,"text":"and this was the guy."},{"time":177000,"text":"\"Fantastic!\" I thought. \"Let's throw him out."},{"time":179000,"text":"Who would ever include a drunken guy in a sample?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":182000,"text":"But a couple of days later,"},{"time":184000,"text":"we thought about it with my students,"},{"time":186000,"text":"and we said, \"What would have happened if this drunken guy was not in that condition?"},{"time":189000,"text":"What would have happened if he was in the other group?"},{"time":191000,"text":"Would we have thrown him out then?\""},{"time":193000,"text":"We probably wouldn't have looked at the data at all,"},{"time":195000,"text":"and if we did look at the data,"},{"time":197000,"text":"we'd probably have said, \"Fantastic! What a smart guy who is performing this low,\""},{"time":200000,"text":"because he would have pulled the mean of the group lower,"},{"time":202000,"text":"giving us even stronger statistical results than we could."},{"time":206000,"text":"So we decided not to throw the guy out and to rerun the experiment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209000,"text":"But you know, these stories,"},{"time":212000,"text":"and lots of other experiments that we've done on conflicts of interest,"},{"time":215000,"text":"basically kind of bring two points"},{"time":217000,"text":"to the foreground for me."},{"time":219000,"text":"The first one is that in life we encounter many people"},{"time":222000,"text":"who, in some way or another,"},{"time":225000,"text":"try to tattoo our faces."},{"time":227000,"text":"They just have the incentives that get them to be blinded to reality"},{"time":230000,"text":"and give us advice that is inherently biased."},{"time":233000,"text":"And I'm sure that it's something that we all recognize,"},{"time":235000,"text":"and we see that it happens."},{"time":237000,"text":"Maybe we don't recognize it every time,"},{"time":239000,"text":"but we understand that it happens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241000,"text":"The most difficult thing, of course, is to recognize"},{"time":243000,"text":"that sometimes we too"},{"time":245000,"text":"are blinded by our own incentives."},{"time":247000,"text":"And that's a much, much more difficult lesson to take into account."},{"time":250000,"text":"Because we don't see how conflicts of interest work on us."},{"time":254000,"text":"When I was doing these experiments,"},{"time":256000,"text":"in my mind, I was helping science."},{"time":258000,"text":"I was eliminating the data"},{"time":260000,"text":"to get the true pattern of the data to shine through."},{"time":262000,"text":"I wasn't doing something bad."},{"time":264000,"text":"In my mind, I was actually a knight"},{"time":266000,"text":"trying to help science move along."},{"time":268000,"text":"But this was not the case."},{"time":270000,"text":"I was actually interfering with the process with lots of good intentions."},{"time":273000,"text":"And I think the real challenge is to figure out"},{"time":275000,"text":"where are the cases in our lives"},{"time":277000,"text":"where conflicts of interest work on us,"},{"time":279000,"text":"and try not to trust our own intuition to overcome it,"},{"time":282000,"text":"but to try to do things"},{"time":284000,"text":"that prevent us from falling prey to these behaviors,"},{"time":286000,"text":"because we can create lots of undesirable circumstances."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290000,"text":"I do want to leave you with one positive thought."},{"time":292000,"text":"I mean, this is all very depressing, right --"},{"time":294000,"text":"people have conflicts of interest, we don't see it, and so on."},{"time":297000,"text":"The positive perspective, I think, of all of this"},{"time":299000,"text":"is that, if we do understand when we go wrong,"},{"time":302000,"text":"if we understand the deep mechanisms"},{"time":304000,"text":"of why we fail and where we fail,"},{"time":306000,"text":"we can actually hope to fix things."},{"time":308000,"text":"And that, I think, is the hope. Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}